    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong>&nbsp;<em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 144</em></p>\n<p><strong>Aura</strong>&nbsp;moderate transmutation&nbsp;<strong>CL</strong>&nbsp;7th</p>\n<p><strong>Slot</strong>&nbsp;weapon quality;&nbsp;<strong>Price</strong>&nbsp;+3,000 gp;&nbsp;<strong>Weight</strong>&nbsp;-</p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\"><img style=\"margin: 3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\" src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" /><strong>Description</strong></h3>\n<p>An&nbsp;<em>impervious&nbsp;</em>weapon is warded from damage and decay. A metallic weapon cannot rust and a wooden weapon cannot rot or warp, even by magical or supernatural means. An&nbsp;<em>impervious</em>&nbsp;weapon gains double the normal bonus to its hardness and hit points for each point of its enhancement bonus. The break DC for an&nbsp;<em>impervious&nbsp;</em>weapon and the wielder's combat maneuver defense against sunder maneuvers against the&nbsp;<em>impervious</em>&nbsp;weapon each gain a bonus equal to twice the weapon's enhancement bonus.</p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong>&nbsp;Craft Magic Arms and Armor,&nbsp;<em>fabricate</em>,&nbsp;<em>make whole</em>;&nbsp;<strong>Price</strong>&nbsp;+1,500 gp</p>",
